InternetBanking-HSBC-UK-Personal version 0.0.1
=============================================

This module provides an interface to the UK personal internet banking
site for HSBC.

It provides the ability to log in, obtain details about accounts (e.g. bank
account number, current balance, account name etc) and also download available
recent transactions ("recent" being the furthest back in time that that the bank
provides).

An example script is provided which illustrates the features of the module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  HTML::TreeBuilder
  WWW::Mechanize

